src:
Hasil FP2 Moto3 Malaysia: Kaito Toba Tercepat di Sepang
01 Nov 2019, 13:10 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Pebalap Honda Team Asia, Kaito Toba, sukses mencatatkan waktu tercepat dalam sesi latihan bebas kedua (FP2) Moto3 Malaysia di Sirkuit Sepang pada Jumat (1/11/2019).
Pebalap Jepang ini diikuti oleh pebalap SIC58 Squadra Corse, Tatsuki Suzuki, di posisi kedua, dan pebalap CIP Moto, Darryn Binder, di posisi ketiga.
Sementara itu posisi keempat dan kelima masing-masing ditempati oleh pebalap Petronas Sprinta Racing, Ayumu Sasaki, dan pebalap Mugen Race, Andrea Migno.
Berikut hasil FP2 Moto3 Malaysia 2019.
text:
Malaysian Moto3 FP2 Results: The Fastest Kaito Toba in Sepang
Nov 01 2019, 13:10 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Honda Team Asia racer Kaito Toba successfully recorded the fastest time in the second free practice session (FP2) Moto3 Malaysia at the Sepang Circuit on Friday (11/01/2019).
The Japanese rider was followed by SIC58 Squadra Corse rider, Tatsuki Suzuki, in second place, and CIP Moto rider Darryn Binder, in third position.
Meanwhile the fourth and fifth positions were each occupied by Sprinta Racing's Petronas racer, Ayumu Sasaki, and Mugen Race's Andrea Migno.
Following are the results of the 2019 Moto3 Malaysia Malaysian.
